Data Dictionary - Draft Picks

Source: vignettes/dictionary_draft_picks.Rmd
dictionary_draft_picks.Rmd
field data_type description
team character Team
pfr_id character PFR player ID
pfr_name character PFR player name
player_id character GSIS player ID (missing for most players)
side character O for offense; D defense; S special teams
category character Player’s position
position character Player’s postition
season numeric Season
round numeric Round selected
pick numeric Overall pick number
